headline: Fee Income & NII to Aid KeyCorp's Q1 Earnings, High Provisions to Hurt
summary: Growth in fee income and NII are likely to have aided KEY's first-quarter 2025 earnings, while higher provisions and elevated expenses are likely to have hurt.
